[[File:Ncwikiquote2.png|frame|right|The Wikiquote logo]]

'''Wikiquote''' is a ''sister'' (related) project of [[Wikipedia]]. It is one of many projects run by the [[Wikimedia Foundation]].

Wikiquote was based on an idea by Daniel Alston and made by Brion Vibber. The goal of the project is to produce a large reference of quotations from famous people, [[book]]s, and [[proverb]]s, and to give details about them.

== Languages ==
The project was first created in [[English language|English]]. However, in July [[2004]], more [[language]]s were added. Some of there are:
