* [[Turkish language]]: [http://tr.wikiquote.org/ Vikisöz]
* [[Urdu language]]: [http://ur.wikiquote.org/ Wikiquote]

As of [[December 25]], [[2010]], 25 versions each have more than 1,000 articles.<ref name="home">[http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Wikiquote#List_of_Wikiquotes List of Wikiquotes on Meta Wiki]</ref> The largest Wikiquote is the English project with over 19,400 content pages,<ref>[http://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Special:Statistics English Wikiquote statistics page]</ref> followed by Polish and Italian versions, both with over 11,000 content pages.<ref>[http://pl.wikiquote.org/wiki/Specjalna:Statystyka Statystyka - Wikicytaty]</ref><ref>[http://it.wikiquote.org/wiki/Speciale:Statistiche Italian Wikiquote statistics page]</ref> In total, 53 languages have over 100 content pages.

In February 2010, the [[Basic English|Simple English]] Wikiquote was locked and closed.

